-- Implementation Blueprint — value shape plus construction and
-- serialisation helpers. The Projector assembles a Blueprint per
-- (primitive, projection-kind) pair; consumers (LLM generators,
-- the Analyzer's verification path) read the resulting record.

use "./blueprint.allium" as blueprint

